Here's a JavaScript function that returns a copy of the input array without any duplicates:

```javascript
function removeDuplicates(arr) {
    let uniqueArray = [];
    for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
        if (uniqueArray.indexOf(arr[i]) === -1) {
            uniqueArray.push(arr[i]);
        }
    }
    return uniqueArray;
}
